      <title>纽约交通局将在收费取消后搁置升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/ny-s-transit-agency-set-to-shelve-upgrades-after-toll-reversal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长凯西·霍楚尔 (Kathy Hochul) 推迟了拥堵收费计划，该计划原本将为改善交通服务提供 150 亿美元的基础设施升级资金，此后，纽约市的交通系统可能会搁置关键的现代化项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/ny-s-transit-agency-set-to-shelve-upgrades-after-toll-reversal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 03:53:28 GMT</pubDate>
